{"tid":1080808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東華教師爆煲】再有東華校長要求老師寫悔過書 疑幾乎迫死老師","createTime":"2019-03-28T00:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T09:34:28.000Z","uid":105003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4ca4b35f2886de6d11d3f49c0cb07d84a691ed","tid":1080808,"uid":105003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:37:20.000Z","msg":"【東華教師爆煲】再有東華校長要求老師寫悔過書 疑幾乎迫死老師<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190328&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59414263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190328%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59414263&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl0y%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=016c52c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190328%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59414263&h=776bbec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190328&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59414263</a><br />\n<br />\n東華三院李東海小學林老師墮樓慘劇，在社會激起千重浪。《蘋果》近日收到教育界多宗求助，揭示林老師生前在校遭受的精神虐待只是冰山一角。本港不少教師長年飽受職場欺凌，有冤無路訴致壓力爆煲，最終企圖自殺、崩潰入院、被迫離職，這些悲劇每天都在校園上演。《蘋果》即日起連載系列報道，本港教師無盡悲歌背後，揭示校本管理失效的種種制度問題。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【東華教師爆煲】兩年11常額教師離職 東華僅將投訴轉交校長<br />\n<br />\n東華三院李東海小學被揭要求林老師撰寫「悔過書」，其「姊妹學校」、同屬東華的姚達之紀念小學（元朗）也涉迫教師寫悔過書。姚達之小學多名教師向《蘋果》控訴，校長羅倩兒經常因小事要求教師寫悔過書，再藉此發警告信迫走資深教師。有教師因遭羅不斷觀課和迫寫悔過書，一度在校內情緒激動欲尋死，在其他教師勸阻下才未有不幸事件發生，其後須接受精神科治療。東華三院則強調，從未要求屬校教師寫悔過書。"},{"pid":"2b5c352451089584b50d03cb92de04a8156da788","tid":1080808,"uid":105003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兩個校長係咪兩姊妹？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c29f9bf0fa7d0ea312a0b3ce9f93fe7d7d5fb37","tid":1080808,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:46:24.000Z","msg":"呢單個老師好彩...<br />\n但個校長實死L梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938cf80bb2b66a6f487eeab9d16ff2a0c683e171","tid":1080808,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c29f9bf0fa7d0ea312a0b3ce9f93fe7d7d5fb37","tid":1080808,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:46:24.000Z","msg":"呢單個老師好彩...<br />\n但個校長實死L梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"點會死<br />\n兩間東華嘅校長換一換位咪得<br />\n又可以繼續作威作福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63daeb14de288e1c7a010746fa5eb9933fa925c5","tid":1080808,"uid":105003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938cf80bb2b66a6f487eeab9d16ff2a0c683e171","tid":1080808,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c29f9bf0fa7d0ea312a0b3ce9f93fe7d7d5fb37","tid":1080808,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:46:24.000Z","msg":"呢單個老師好彩...<br />\n但個校長實死L梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"點會死<br />\n兩間東華嘅校長換一換位咪得<br />\n又可以繼續作威作福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"大家都姓羅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1154108d3fca48704cde7cc3f740c1ce3005e96d","tid":1080808,"uid":94054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"好似十幾廿年前姚達之係正校<br />\n轉晒全日制之後, 下午校就去李東海上堂<br />\n會唔會兩個校長夾埋"}]}